		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />And for the record, this is what you'd like to insert into LocalSettings.php:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">$wgGroupPermissions&#91;'*'&#93;&#91;'createaccount'&#93; = false;<br />$wgGroupPermissions&#91;'*'&#93;&#91;'edit'&#93; = false;<br />$wgGroupPermissions&#91;'user'&#93;&#91;'edit'&#93; = false;<br />$wgGroupPermissions&#91;'sysop'&#93;&#91;'edit'&#93; = true;</div>You could replace the last <em>true</em> with <em>false</em> if you want <strong>absolutely nobody</strong> to edit pages.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
